{"word":"Absalom","slug":"absalom","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Absalom</b> - the son of David<p/><b>(1)</b> General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=3'>2Sa 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=29'>2Sa 13:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=37'>2Sa 13:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=25'>2Sa 14:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=2'>2Sa 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=14'>2Sa 15:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=1'>2Sa 17:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=9'>2Sa 18:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=14'>2Sa 18:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=33'>2Sa 18:33</a><p/><b>(2)</b> FACTS CONCERNING<p/>Born of a polygamous marriage<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=3'>2Sa 3:3</a><p/>Murders his brother<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=29'>2Sa 13:29</a><p/>An exile from home<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=37'>2Sa 13:37</a><p/>Renowned for his beauty<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=25'>2Sa 14:25</a><p/>The designing politician<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=2'>2Sa 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=3'>2Sa 15:3</a><p/>Conspires against his father, David<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=13'>2Sa 15:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=14'>2Sa 15:14</a><p/>Comes to an untimely end<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=9'>2Sa 18:9</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Young Men, YOUNG PEOPLE"}]}